    <briefdescription>
<para>Logger multidomain backend helpers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This module aims to provide baseline for links and backends and simplify the implementation. It is not core part of logging in similar way as <ref refid="structlog__output" kindref="compound">log_output</ref> module is just a helper for log message formatting. Links and backends can be implemented without this helper. </para>
